OL,3,CBBC sanctioned over Gaza documentary
OL,4,Cfor 'serious' broadcasting breach
OL,6,FThe BBC has been found to have
OL,7,Fcommitted a "serious breach" of
OL,8,Fbroadcasting rules after failing to
OL,9,Fdisclose that the narrator of a
OL,10,Fdocumentary on Gaza was the son of a
OL,11,FHamas official, UK watchdog Ofcom has
OL,12,Fruled.
OL,14,FThe documentary Gaza: How to Survive a
OL,15,FWarzone was removed from BBC iPlayer
OL,16,Fin February after it emerged that the
OL,17,Fchild narrator, Abdullah, is the son
OL,18,Fof Ayman Alyazouri, who has served as
OL,19,FHamas's deputy minister of agriculture.
