OL,3,CBBC sanctioned over Gaza documentary
OL,4,Cfor 'serious' broadcasting breach
OL,6,FIt was made for the BBC by the
OL,7,Findependent production company Hoyo
OL,8,FFilms.
OL,10,FOfcom said the BBC's failure to
OL,11,Fdisclose this information "was
OL,12,Fmaterially misleading" as "it had the
OL,13,Fpotential to erode the very high
OL,14,Flevels of trust audiences would have
OL,15,Fexpected in a BBC factual programme
OL,16,Fabout the Israel-Gaza war".
OL,18,FAs a result of the breach, the BBC
OL,19,Fwill face sanctions by being ordered
OL,20,Fto broadcast the Ofcom findings.
