OL,3,CBBC sanctioned over Gaza documentary
OL,4,Cfor 'serious' broadcasting breach
OL,6,FIn February, a letter to BBC director-
OL,7,Fgeneral Tim Davie from public figures,
OL,8,Fincluding Friday Night Dinner actress
OL,9,FTracy-Ann Oberman, called on the BBC
OL,10,Fto remove the documentary from
OL,11,FiPlayer, due to concerns over its
OL,12,F"editorial standards".
OL,14,FLater that month, the BBC said an
OL,15,Finitial review had found "serious
OL,16,Fflaws" in the programme and announced
OL,17,Fa full fact-finding investigation led
OL,18,Fby its director of Editorial
OL,19,FComplaints and Reviews, Peter Johnston.
