OL,3,CBBC sanctioned over Gaza documentary
OL,4,Cfor 'serious' broadcasting breach
OL,6,FA BBC spokesperson said: "The Ofcom
OL,7,Fruling is in line with the findings of
OL,8,FPeter Johnston's review, that there
OL,9,Fwas a significant failing in the
OL,10,Fdocumentary in relation to the BBC's
OL,11,Feditorial guidelines on accuracy,
OL,12,Fwhich reflects Rule 2.2 of Ofcom's
OL,13,FBroadcasting Code.
OL,15,F"We have apologised for this and we
OL,16,Faccept Ofcom's decision in full.
OL,18,F"We will comply with the sanction as
OL,19,Fsoon as the date and wording are
OL,20,Ffinalised."
